NATURE OF PROCEEDINGS: Order to Show Cause Re: Failure to File Proof of Service
The Order to Show Cause is not called for hearing.
There is no appearance by or for the plaintiff.
The court makes orders as follows:
Order to Show Cause Re: Imposition of Monetary Sanctions in an Amount of up to $250.00 on
Plaintiff Pursuant to C.C.P., Section 177.5, for Failure to Timely File Proof of Service as to
Defendant, Cheng (SECOND SETTING) is scheduled for 08/06/25 at 8:30 AM in Department V
at Alhambra Courthouse.
Order to Show Cause Re: Dismissal Pursuant to C.C.P. Sections 581(b)(4), 583.110 and 583.130
and/or Sanctions of up to $250.00 Pursuant to C.C.P., 177.5; for Failure of Plaintiff to Attend

Courthouse.

advanced to this date and continued to 08/06/25 at 08:30 AM in Department V at Alhambra
Courthouse.
